Class Schemes

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.isr.data.Schemes

  • class Schemes
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the weighting schemes. Each scheme defines the importance of each instance based on a distance notion.

        static double proximity(Instance inst,

        Weigh an instance based on the proximity of the k nearest neighbors in the input or in the input-output space, defined as the average distance from the instance to its k nearest neighbors.
